<br>
I had someone ask my gray-haired, scarred dwarf warrior what happened to his family the other day.  I said, ‘Oh, mother and father are still rattling around in Kaladim.  My wife and daughter are living with them.’<br>
<br>
They were horrified.<br>
<br>
Of course, in the EQ world, it’s almost inconceivable that anyone would be an orphan anyway:<br>
<br>
“Alas!  My parents died when I was young!”<br>
<br>
“And when didn’t they come to get you when they re-spawned?”<br>
<br>
“Uh…”<br>
<br>
“Weren’t they bound nearby?”<br>
<br>
“Er…”<br>
